                            <comment id="211685" author="bogl" created="Mon, 23 Oct 2017 15:15:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;All the relevant mods have landed to b2_8_fe:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/29596&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/29596&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/29639&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/29639&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
